[TranslatorEvent0]
Message="The Krall arrived probably from the mystic mountains. There are plenty of rumors about the mysterious ring. Only one who might know something, is a recluse with a small house in the mountains, just ahead of the temple."
M_NewMessage="Prison notes"
M_TransMessage="Prison notes"

[Trigger0]
