[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="I was captured durring the attack on the village and brought here. In a nearby cell is a foreigner from another world. Sometimes we talked through a hole between the bricks. He wanted to warn us of an attack of the Krall. He told me also, that his planet had been conquered by them with the help of yet another race."
M_NewMessage="Nali notes"
M_TransMessage="Nali notes"

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="I stole this object on the planet Taros. It's some kind of a shield, that could make the wearer immortal. Until the energy of the shield is exhausted."
M_NewMessage="Old book"
M_TransMessage="Old book"

[TranslatorEvent7]
Message="Long ago Paci sent us these little boxes. Inside are silver looking wheels. We do not know what they are. He mentioned something about a metal?"
M_NewMessage="Small book"
M_TransMessage="Small book"

[TranslatorEvent3]
Message="In this temple we were ambushed by the Krall. My friend has been dragged into a jail. I managed to get here. I found the gun ASMD, but it was a trap from which I could not leave. My death is coming."
M_NewMessage="Notes of a dead stranger"
M_TransMessage="Notes of a dead stranger"

[TranslatorEvent2]
Message="I managed to close the bars and prevent a progress of additional enemies. When I was returning, one Krall waited in the shadows and surprised me. I hope that I can get out, before I die."
M_NewMessage="Dead Nali notes"
M_TransMessage="Dead Nali notes"

[Trigger1]
Message="Green triangle activated."

[SpecialEvent7]
Message="Something tells me, that I should save the game in a new slot."

