Message="Our planet was conquered by the Krall with the help of the Skaarj. And now they are preparing to do the same to planet Madehiten. I went with my friend through the gate to warn Madehiten. I was captured, but I hope that my friend can warn them in time..."
M_NewMessage="Notes of a dead stranger"
M_TransMessage="Notes of a dead stranger"

[Trigger2]
